.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, spy, animation, musical
House: gothic-revival, cape-cod, futuristic, modern
4 different pets are kept: fish, frog, mouse, rabbit
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, snowboarding, tennis, weightlifting
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, subway, tram, trike
 1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 3. the person watching animation movies is the owner of the rabbit##1
 4. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 5. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
 6. the person driving the trike is the person watching animation movies##1
 7. the futuristic house is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 8. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 9. the modern house is the owner of the frog##1
10. the cape-cod house is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
11. the person driving the trike is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
12. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3    |       4       |
| Movie-Genre          | epic    | musical      | animation  | spy   |
| House   | modern     | futuristic      | cape-cod | gothic-revival      |
| Pet           | frog       | fish         | rabbit  | mouse         |
| Sport         | basketball | snowboarding | tennis  | weightlifting |
| Transport     | tram       | bike         | trike   | subway        |

