.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, water-polo, weightlifting, snowboarding
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, november, october, january
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, journalist, musician, teacher
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, canadian, spanish, turkish
4 different pets are kept: bird, ferret, lizard, snake
 1. the dancer is the owner of the snake##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far left##1
 3. the canadian is on the far right##1
 4. the owner of the ferret is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 5. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 6. the musician is on the far right##1
 7. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 8. the owner of the snake is the dancer##1
 9. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the owner of the lizard##1
10. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
11. the australian is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
12. the journalist is on the far left##1
13. the australian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
14. the spanish is on the right of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Sport          | skiing       | water-polo     | weightlifting     | snowboarding  |
| Birthday         | october  | january | may | november  |
| Job           | journalist | dancer    | teacher    | musician |
| Nationality   | turkish    | spanish   | australian | canadian |
| Pet           | bird       | snake     | ferret     | lizard   |

