 6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left##1
 7. the security-guard is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 8. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the fisherman##1
 9. the pall-mall-smoker is the person driving the subway##1
10. the blend-smoker is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
11. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
12. the baccarat-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2        |      3      |      4       |
| Cigar    | pall-mall     | fonseca  | blend       | baccarat      |
| Hobby       | singing    | writing        | collecting  | drawing      |
| Job         | fisherman  | security-guard | firefighter | photographer |
| Flower         | amaryllis | lily          | balloon-flower         | bellflower      |
| Transport   | subway     | helicopter     | trike       | van          |

