 8. the cape-cod house is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 9. the owner of the chinchilla is the person who growslily##1
10. the person who growslily is on the far left##1
11. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
12. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1

